quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,76,"Soni chisimu chalakwechi ni chilumbilo chekulungwa nnope ingaŵe mwamanyililaga."
  56,77,"Chisimu jalakweji ni Qur’an jakuchimbichika."
  56,78,"Jili m’Chitabu chesunjidwe chenene (Al-Lauh Al- Mahfȗz)."
  67,16,"Ana nkuiona kuti n'di pantunjelele mwanti (Allah) Jwaali kwinani ngaŵa nkuntitimisya nalyo litaka, basi nikuŵa lyalakwelyo lina nkutenganyika (pakuwowochelwa)?"
  67,17,"Kapena nkuiona kuti n'di pantunjelele mwanti (Allah) Jwaali kwinani ngaŵa nkuntumichisya chimbunga chasakalawe (nikun'jonanga nasyo sakalawesyo)? Basi ni tinchimanyilila mwachikasaŵelaga chitetelo Changu."
  67,18,"Soni yakuonaonape pamasile paŵaakaaniile aŵala ŵapaujo pao, nambi kwaliji uli kasilika Kwangu (ngati najonasile wosope)?"
  68,10,"Soni ngasimumpikanila jwalijose jwakulumbila-lumbila soni jwakwaluka."
  68,11,"Nkusogoda, jwakwendajenda kupita nchitenda unakunaku."
  68,12,"Jwakusiŵilila yambone, jwakusumba mpika, jwasambi syejinji."
  69,7,"(Allah) ŵajitumisye kukwao yilo nsano naiŵili ni muusi nsano nautatu mwakulundanya, mwanti nkaweni ŵandu mwalakwemo ali jajaja! Nti chisawu mapata ga itela yatende gangali chachipali nkati mwakwe."
  69,8,"Nambi kwali nkum'bona mwa ŵanganyao jwalijose jwasigele?"
  69,9,"Nombe Afiriauna kwisa soni ŵandu ŵa paujo pakwe ni achinsyene misi jajapitikusyidwe (ŵandu ŵa Lutwi) ŵayiche ni ilemwa."
  70,1,"Jwawusisye nkuwusya (mwachipongwe) yailagasyo yakupatikana (kuti: Tiyipatikane chakachi?)."
  70,2,"Kwa achimakafili pangali jwampaka ayisiŵilile."
  70,3,"Yakuumila kwa Allah Nsyene Makwelelo."